➜湖北诗人木子：五律·秋（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/427905260_100115135	33199
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201028/ac43d432e1ba4cae87b68c576cda95e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五律·秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冷雨续添愁，丹枫尽醉眸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杯中藏冷暖，笔下弃恩仇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">展卷千行泪，挥桡万里舟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清泉何处觅，落叶自知秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201028/8cea09db3cbe4a8396370d99b0582bdb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋游</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋暮，霜欲下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">方觉衣衫薄寒意浓</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
