➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：致雪藻兰襟精舍
http://www.sohu.com/a/427907299_100115135	33669
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/e86b56a787a0419fa6fe1a904fd33eb3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>致雪藻兰襟精舍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爬上山，林森曲径通幽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书山有路，更精进</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雪藻精舍立成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朝拜，如入寺虔诚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拿什么礼物给你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我有思泉引墨入池磨砚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写敬词恭祝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>取红柿之喜庆漾笑门楣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掏出丹叶里住了一夏的太阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做燃料点燃心炉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">借秋枫扇焰，冶炼文字钢精</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笔尖雕砌诗画廊亭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>磨石凿玉，霞落雁归时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你可知我折叠储存有许多月亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>做了圆圆压缩饼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>送给精舍，喂饱黑夜的眼睛</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
