➜听尘居士：问天
http://www.sohu.com/a/427909068_100115135	34033
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201028/c07602e9a8d94ff1b8634c91a8cdeabc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>问天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/听尘居士</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞梦寻花柳岸荫，长歌一曲断红尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未得丹华轻眷顾，回首已成百年身。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我向晴天泪染血，总将瑶台逐孤魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一袭青衣做草寇，何必高谈论古今。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/73707528bbe44f59b89dbe11d7f84eb5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>听尘居士，原名牛喜忠。吉林籍，现居深圳。半生无所成，流浪江湖。偶弄笔墨，未有一名。闲了拈花惹草，迎来半院春色；静时参禅打坐，佛道一通乱修。朋友小聚可品香茗，饮自酿美酒，临厨而成美食。唯不懂人间烟火，只好浪迹天涯一隅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201028/d629ec39ea80492ca92cbcd7c9ca9cad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
