➜广东诗人欧大象：重阳登勾髻岭
http://www.sohu.com/a/427911060_100115135	34574
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201028/619cc26462244b5ba345e37fd7fc6d1d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳登勾髻岭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/欧大象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重阳结伴去郊游，直上凌霄盘髻头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艳丽娘们如逸兔，古稀老汉似灵猴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身披鹤雾衣衫白，树挂霜珠曲径幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">极目春州寻胜景，拨开云海万山秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>庚子重阳节</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201028/01955679c9094947973390fba8690b87.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题黄云故居联</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/欧大象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">齐心打造黄金路；</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
